{"tid":613670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預言：曾發表港獨、反共言論者，公司將不會聘用！","createTime":"2018-04-02T00:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T23:21:17.000Z","uid":29314,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a36f434833c01b8179f4f0dcef5d93602f3cfb6","tid":613670,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"曾發表港獨、反共言論者，不得參加所有本地主辦之公開試，包括但不限DSE！<br />\n<br />\n曾發表港獨、反共言論者，本地機構及上市公司將不會聘用！<br />\n<br />\n曾發表港獨、反共言論者，將不會獲得特區政府任何房屋福利！<br />\n<br />\n曾發表港獨、反共言論者，將不會獲發特區護照、回鄉證、及其他旅行證件！"},{"pid":"399c07cab3c975f0e6e13f51fa14101590713439","tid":613670,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:56:37.000Z","msg":"好多年前已經話有人事部會審查facebook"},{"pid":"8c4c21c9d6d24d48c49aa27c4494a1d98a1f52b2","tid":613670,"uid":29804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"個Facebook <br />\n乜鳩都冇"},{"pid":"faf2c0c827859583163ef715311621b2698c8601","tid":613670,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多年前已經話有人事部會審查facebook</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n止唔止facebook，仲有其他呢"},{"pid":"ab9bbd765f4fcf94b927faaaaf379c39c8f10830","tid":613670,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"399c07cab3c975f0e6e13f51fa14101590713439","tid":613670,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T00:56:37.000Z","msg":"好多年前已經話有人事部會審查facebook"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"#deletefacebook"},{"pid":"8664788aaf3c90fb43656773d75ecba84b8ac92b","tid":613670,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"已經預算左兩年後失業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79067d2ecabb3fa603da186d2e5d3284ef056d04","tid":613670,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a